4cb46ae1-44b0-4b35-9aaf-f3e42b584d05.name: Wake Park Varna
4cb46ae1-44b0-4b35-9aaf-f3e42b584d05.info:
Wake Park Varna is the first and only wake park in Varna and on the north coast of The Black Sea in Bulgaria. 
You can ride with your own equipment or rent from the park. They also offer wakeboarding lessons.
There are two lines - one for beginners and one for more advanced riders.

3a400d08-c81d-4259-8ca3-1f30e6ac7e91.name: Park X Plovdiv
3a400d08-c81d-4259-8ca3-1f30e6ac7e91.info: Park X Plovdiv is a wakepark featuring 3 x Two Tower Systems and SHAPE obstacles: 4 x kickers, roller pop off, rooftop, wedge rail, curve slider and 20 m straight pipe.
